text: The space what a great amount of room and space. The Lyft trip was close to downtown and about the price in the listing. Check in was a breeze since Taylor arranged key pickup, which was nice. The airbnb listing didn't provide the direct location, which caused a bit of confusion prior to check in the day of, the address and map were two different locations. After a direct text to Taylor that was quickly resolved.
title: Cozy Space Close to City
